{"tid":966241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會又派錢","createTime":"2019-01-02T15:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T08:01:37.000Z","uid":91230,"like":111,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"52756db6848ad50693f83ed546100ff84f67554c","tid":966241,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"今次馬會真係開錯盤派錢<br />\n<br />\n利而家個勢 一睇就知係不敗奪冠<br />\n鏝就算主場都冇太大優勢<br />\n地理位置嚟講 曼市同利物浦根本就喺隔離<br />\n利都當咗半個主場嚟打<br />\n再加上近期鏝主場都可以輸俾水晶宮<br />\n就知鏝喺主場都係會俾猁㩒住嚟打<br />\n<br />\n馬會咁都開3.25客勝<br />\n其實等於派錢<br />\n就算你怕利好保守求和<br />\n讓盤都仲有2.07倍<br />\n真係怕嘅 仲有讓球1.78倍<br />\n<br />\n我就借咗一千萬買客勝<br />\n約咗經紀星期五睇樓<br />\n咁多位巴打<br />\n做人做狗自己揀"},{"pid":"747fcb52b134050959804c17792c257b9c7785b4","tid":966241,"uid":108545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"留名又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fbc74f98b6eb28e67da6202ccf4a7cdb3717d0","tid":966241,"uid":57346,"like":10,"dislike":24,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEo3a4L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEo3a4L.png&h=47282a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nok gun"},{"pid":"444a958a7088048134f5edf2c6dd3cccb71ca3ae","tid":966241,"uid":22115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c92a5e3217bd3bdf623104a50162c62b30dbef7","tid":966241,"uid":91230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"51fbc74f98b6eb28e67da6202ccf4a7cdb3717d0","tid":966241,"uid":57346,"like":10,"dislike":24,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEo3a4L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEo3a4L.png&h=47282a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nok gun"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:46:03.00